{
  "stem": "166.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they started grabbing people from the street, whoever they see, on the trucks and sent them to camps or to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In order not to go, you had to have a special pass, and they had blue-- some kind-- I had a, a card, a blue card.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] How did I get this blue card?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We used to live in a house-- there was-- after 7 o'clock we couldn't go out anymore.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we lived in an apartment house where there was a neighbor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He used to have an electrical store.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after 7 o'clock in the evening, the neighbors got together.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was nothing to do.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They talked politics, and they played cards.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the neighbor-- we asked the neighbor to do a favor, maybe you can take him, my boy, into work.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I went into work for him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he had a [GERMAN], they called it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All the Jewish businesses were taken away from the Jews, and they put in a German in the business, that he is the whole manager for the business, and he was the boss.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the owner worked for that boss now, for the, for the German.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that [GERMAN] had three electrical stores, and through him I got into a store where I became an electrician.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- but by becoming electrician, I became-- I had a blue card, and on the blue card was written, from the SS, [SPEAKING GERMAN]",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With this blue card, I was safe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it's very hard for me to translate this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a division that they took care for, for foreigners-- for foreign, for foreign war commanders in East Upper Silesia-- division of something from the SS.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
